01b[Ceep using Fable 5 with usage credits, or switch\u001b[Cto\u001b[Canother\u001b[17;4Hmodel\u001b[Cto\u001b[Ckeep\u001b[Cworking\u001b[Cwithin\u001b[Cyour\u001b[Cremaining\u001b[Climits.\u001b[18;4H\u001b[K\nM\u001b[Cr\u001b[C details here: https://suppo\u001b[Ct.cl\u001b[Cude.com/en/articles/15424964-claude-fable-5-promotional-access\u001b[20;2H\u001b[K\r\n\u001b[38;5;239m\u001b[48;5;237m\u276f \u001b[38;5;231mAdd one short joke about credentials to jokes.md, then commit it, push it, and open a pull request. This is issue #202.\u001b[39m                                       \u001b[23;1H\u001b[49m\u001b[38;5;231m\u25cf\u001b[39m I'll start by looking at the current state of jokes.md.\u001b[K\u001b[25;1H\u001b[38;5;246m \u001b[C\u001b[39mRunning \u001b[1m1\u001b[m\u000f shel\u001b[C command\u2026\u001b[C\u001b[K\u001b[27;1H\u001b[38;5;174m*\u001b[CD\u001b[10C\u001b[38;5;246m(3s \u00b7 \u2193\u001b[C2 tokens)\u001b[30;3H\u001b[m\u000f"]
